      "title": "Periodic Solutions to Non-Autonomous Second-Order Systems",
      "abstract": "Abstract We establish the existence of periodic solution of a class of non-autonomous second-order systems, x + μ x + V ( t , x ) = 0 , where V ( t , x ) = ( v 1 ( t , x ) , … , v n ( t , x ) ) , if lim | x | → ∞ v i ( t , x ) | x | = 0 , i = 1 , … , n , uniformly in t and V is bounded below or above for appropriate ranges of μ ."
